{"tid":139580,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實香港人廣東人有無中東血統？","createTime":"2017-03-01T13:56:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-02T08:28:20.000Z","uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"01793070a95b216b36c7f6e817a697aab1db7a05","tid":139580,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T13:56:40.000Z","msg":"相傳唐朝定宋朝時期，曾經試過有成十萬大食人係廣東到，而廣東人口亦都只係一百萬左右<br />\n<br />\n換言之，十個就有一個大食人<br />\n<br />\n其實廣東人有無承繼到呢堆人嘅血統<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710345e81fc9bf6958a5c3d6c44036cf5039e4b3","tid":139580,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T15:27:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83740c7a7f3113e9ec25f66c4bd87a5f574748cc","tid":139580,"uid":27663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T15:33:51.000Z","msg":"有都唔出奇<br />\n不過考究唔到啦應該"},{"pid":"659fc7f801e63fd2ecd6983e77b364b8050e5c9c","tid":139580,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T15:36:03.000Z","msg":"又真係有啲人係黑啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0520e87060d13bec429d6eed8d328e46fd9a3161","tid":139580,"uid":24378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T15:38:59.000Z","msg":"有呀，巫婆琳未有囉"},{"pid":"f86b8bf28b1979eff08ffcbe6830327d367b1142","tid":139580,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T16:12:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有都唔出奇<br />\n不過考究唔到啦應該</blockquote><br />\n照道理，當時十萬個中東佬，除非戰亂將佢地全部殺晒，如果唔係好難無混入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6b7355a678dc5a3f712323489fb638bfe5bed9e","tid":139580,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T16:14:25.000Z","msg":"因為我研究面相，日日望下唔同人個樣嘅時候，發現好多人兩條眉都係連埋，而好多中東人條眉都係連埋嘅"},{"pid":"945bab521f37c9286c3b7b6b057dbf06467c4a7e","tid":139580,"uid":52349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T19:28:36.000Z","msg":"孫中山？<br />\n輪廓唔多似東亞人"},{"pid":"337ec4ca3ecfcbefc919b904174dc629fa6e1c4a","tid":139580,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T02:48:19.000Z","msg":"黃巢殺哂啦？"},{"pid":"077ea6dc7ab73cfa690e3a6a3e95b06a1352c028","tid":139580,"uid":27663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T08:28:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黃巢殺哂啦？</blockquote><br />\n宋朝嗰堆殺唔到掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n印象中通常係四川/中原地區比較多人口滅絕，廣東好似唔多"}]}